{"title": "The Genesis of Generative with DCA", "slug": "the-genesis-of-generative-with-dca", "date": "2024-11-28", "author": "theline1", "excerpt": "", "categories": ["1/1", "Art Blocks Curated", "generative", "mintface collection", "on-chain", "Series One"], "featuredImage": "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62.png", "images": ["https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1320x990.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-768x582.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-768x438.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1320x990.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-600x455.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1024x780.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-768x576.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1536x1170.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-600x450.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-600x342.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-300x225.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-300x225.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1024x776.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-600x450.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1024x768.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1024x768.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-400x300.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-400x300.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-768x585.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-300x227.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1536x1164.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1024x584.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-2048x1536.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1320x1006.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1320x1000.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1536x1152.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-768x576.webp", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1320x753.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-600x457.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1536x1152.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-300x229.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1536x876.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-300x171.png"], "content": "<h2>The Artist: Daniel Calderon (DCA)</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The beginning of generative art on Art Blocks started on Day Zero. The first day of minting art as crispy ERC-721 tokens on the Art Blocks smart contract. Sure you can point to the first on-chain generative art, <a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/larva-labs/\">Autoglyphs by Larva Labs</a> as preceding Art Blocks by 3+ years. You can also argue that the timestamped provenance of <a href=\"https://theline.wtf/generative-cryptoarte-with-seb-broucher/\">Cryptoarte by Seb Broucher</a> pre-dates Autoglyphs. Going further, you can also argue that generative art existed for decades earlier thanks to digital art pioneers like Vera Molnár. But...Art Blocks was first to provide a platform for <em>all </em>generative artists to share their generative art on-chain.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1024x768.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1024x768.webp 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-300x225.webp 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-768x576.webp 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-400x300.webp 400w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-1320x990.webp 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png-600x450.webp 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1000000.png.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Genesis #0 by DCA collected by DCInvestor</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Hash strings and algorithms are my bread and butter. I use generative art to explore randomness.\" \t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Daniel Calderon Arenas (DCA)</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Genesis (Art Blocks Curated)</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Genesis was one of three Art Blocks collections minted on Day Zero of the Art Blocks generative art revolution, November 28th 2020, alongside Chromie Squiggles and Construction Token. The description of the Genesis art collection is primarily educational because few understood what minting art meant. \"Genesis: Generative System. A block hash string is interpreted into a visual composition using a set of algorithmic rules. Compositions may contain grids, gradients, lines, shapes, and colors that harmonize with each other. Each mint is one of a kind and designed to stand-alone. Limited Edition.\"</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"571\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1024x780.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1024x780.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-300x229.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-768x585.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1536x1170.png 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-1320x1006.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-600x457.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA.png 1898w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>'Curve', 'Dots' and 'Special' provide some of the more interesting rarity traits. 'White Sprinkles' (25) and 'Soft Points' (22) variants of 'Dots' (47) are the salt bae Genesis works of the collection. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"568\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1024x776.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1024x776.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-300x227.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-768x582.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1536x1164.png 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-1320x1000.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots-600x455.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-by-DCA-dots.png 1906w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>'Glowing Bezier' (13) variant of 'Curve' trait (99) is clearly visually identifiable as through a flair a white signature like expression. The Glowing Bezier (13) is the grail trait variant in the collection, admired and collected by MintFace and 6529Museum.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1024x584.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1024x584.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-300x171.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-768x438.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1536x876.png 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-1320x753.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA-600x342.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-collection-glowing-bezier-DCA.png 1904w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Genesis with 'Glowing Bezier' trait variant</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Genesis #62</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Genesis #62 exhibits the 'Glowing Bezier' trait prominently. First minted by NateAlex on November 28th 2020; Day Zero for the Art Blocks, on-chain explosion that was to come. Genesis #62 displays one 'RECT1' rectangle, and one 'RECT2' rectangle along with a barely perceptible 'Colored Trapezoid' variant. The 'Grid' pattern diagonally covers the art. We are yet to see the more organic, flowing, curvy styles that come to be admired by generative art collectors, yet the 'Glowing Bezier' trait variant in Genesis #62 hints at the possibilities of code as art to come.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1024x768.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1024x768.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-300x225.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-768x576.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1536x1152.png 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-2048x1536.png 2048w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-400x300.png 400w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-1320x990.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/genesis-62-600x450.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Art Blocks Curated Genesis #62 by DCA collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>"}